<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Aura | Experience Sound</title>
    <style>
        /* Modern Reset & Base Styles */
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { 
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; 
            background-color: #fafafa; 
            color: #1a1a1a;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Layout */
        .container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }
        
        header { padding: 40px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.5rem; letter-spacing: -1px; }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero { padding: 100px 0; text-align: center; }
        h1 { font-size: 4rem; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; letter-spacing: -2px; }
        p.subtitle { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #666; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 40px; }

        /* Button */
        .btn { 
            background: #000; color: #fff; padding: 16px 32px; 
            text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; 
            font-weight: 600; transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .btn:hover { background: #333; transform: scale(1.05); }

        /* Visual Element (Placeholder for Product Image) */
        .product-preview { 
            width: 100%; height: 400px; background: #e0e0e0; 
            margin-top: 60px; border-radius: 20px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: #888; font-weight: 500;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <div class="logo">AURA.</div>
            <nav>Shop</nav>
        </header>

        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Sound, neu definiert.</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Erlebe kristallklare Akustik in einem Design, das perfekt zu deinem Lebensstil passt. Deine Musik, ohne Kompromisse.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn">Jetzt entdecken</a>

            <div class="product-preview">
                [Produktbild hier einfügen]
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
